title: # 32 – Something’s Burning Uncut – Kyle Kinane & Matt Braunger
description:
Something’s Burning Uncut is the uncut audio from my cooking show “Something’s Burning” on YouTube.

On this episode that originally aired on YouTube Oct 28, 2019, Kyle Kinane, Matt Braunger and I make Bourbon Maple Cocktails.
